<br>
Killed one Last night on the Way to wasteing the Named Croc. It dropped a Etherial Parchment. Name Croc Didnt Drop Spell stuffs but the stats on his combat are ----<br>
<br>
32k Hp <br>
No AoE<br>
He Doubles For 1136 <br>
After Discussion We called in another Cleric for total of 2<br>
Raid consisted of.<br>
2 Warrior <br>
3 Magician <br>
2 Bard <br>
1 Shaman <br>
1 Ranger <br>
2 Cleric <br>
2 Druids<br>
2 Necro<br>
1 SK<br>
Had we known what his HP were we would have planned differently. Very eay Mob once he is slowed and Crippled.<br>
<br>
Drops a Nice 11 18 1hs with a few stats. Nice Drop seems to be a Statue equivlent Loot table. Second Drop<br>
was a ac14 Shaman Druid BL only Green Skin Jerkin or some sort ac14 +10wis Stam dex 40mana 40hp +15mr,pr,dr. Not all too hatefull.<br>
<br>
Once we Saw his lack of HP we decided to Nuke at 60% and be done with him. With proper Preperation he is deffinatly a 2 group Mob. Happy Hunting.<br>
<br>
Back to the Consorts. They are the Big Spiders along the wall in PoN. Near the Ruins / Second Graveyard. hit pretty hard for about 400 max per attack and have approx 32k+ HP each. Fight last about 2 mins or so give or take. But in one kill it had one spell part so maybe we were lucky.<br>
<br>
Tyvalius Valthalion <br>
